{
  "page": "Huzhor Amai",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Huzhor Amai<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Amazing</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Sarnor\" title=\"Kingdom of Sarnor\">Kingdom of Sarnor</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Amazing</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tall_Men\" title=\"Tall Men\">Tall Men</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tall_Men\" title=\"Tall Men\">Tall Men</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouses</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Cymmeri\" title=\"Cymmeri\">Cymmeri</a> wife</li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Gipps\" title=\"Gipps\">Gipp</a> wife</li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Zoqora\" title=\"Zoqora\">Zoqora</a> wife</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Huzhor Amai</b>, called <b>the Amazing</b>, is a legendary hero and ancestor of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tall_Men\" title=\"Tall Men\">Tall Men</a>, the nation that founded the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Sarnor\" title=\"Kingdom of Sarnor\">Kingdom of Sarnor</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Huzhor_Amai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to legend, he was born of the last of the <a href=\"/index.php/Fisher_Queens\" title=\"Fisher Queens\">Fisher Queens</a> and took to wife the daughters of the greatest lords and kings of the <a href=\"/index.php/Gipps\" title=\"Gipps\">Gipps</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Cymmeri\" title=\"Cymmeri\">Cymmeri</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Zoqora\" title=\"Zoqora\">Zoqora</a>. His Zoqora wife drove his <a href=\"/index.php/Chariot\" title=\"Chariot\">chariot</a>, and his Cymmeri wife made his armor. He also wore about his shoulders a great cloak made from the pelt of a king of the <a href=\"/index.php/Hairy_Men\" title=\"Hairy Men\">Hairy Men</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Huzhor_Amai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Grasslands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403233316\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.062 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.250 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 523/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10883/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6128/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 750/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 687/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  243.419      1 -total\n 97.49%  237.316      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 96.88%  235.836      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.19%   29.683     14 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.76%   14.032      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.87%    4.543      1 Template:Ref\n  1.05%    2.559      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.58%    1.411      1 Template:References\n  0.49%    1.189      2 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19488-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403233316 and revision id 311664\n -->\n",
